11 . 
    Go to line 9 by typing :9 and pressing Enter.
    Enter visual line mode by pressing V (that’s uppercase ‘v’).
    Cut the line by pressing d.
    Go to line 5 by typing :5 and pressing Enter.
    Paste the line above line 5 by pressing P (that’s uppercase ‘p’).
